    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those licensed and appointed to steer ships while arriving or departing a port, or through local waters until those ships reach their destination or open sea. The license issued to maritime pilots is specific to particular areas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
